{"tid":1628404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做人冇PR 食得屎啦","createTime":"2019-10-06T02:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T02:44:10.000Z","uid":151277,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58d5ae3975e722b9a41494d262d0a443bc0dcf09","tid":1628404,"uid":151277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:42:58.000Z","msg":"又唔係叫你唔做 叫你做少日 叫你用下個腦先做<br />\n裝修裝錯左仲聲大夾惡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇人唔記得啲狗點樣開槍殺我地手足 點樣將佢地拉入新屋嶺到打同被自殺<br />\n<br />\n但係做時要睇時機<br />\n<br />\n宜家係向全世界展示林鄭用緊急法推禁蒙面法係唔合理嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n你要裝修咪聽日後日聽晚後晚囉<br />\n<br />\n係咪想個世界見到林鄭想佢地睇到嘅畫面？<br />\n<br />\n難聽啲咁講句 宜家死係好撚易 但係做到全球支持條命先死得有價值<br />\n<br />\n國際線手足嘅努力都唔好白廢左佢 好冇？"},{"pid":"00817d22f31e5c908588b76fffd05d92fe8f804d","tid":1628404,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:43:22.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=6d5fc44d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a>"},{"pid":"b6fb1e7d412d75a8b4d006ea9ccdbb524dc5af35","tid":1628404,"uid":141270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:44:10.000Z","msg":"形象係一件好重要嘅事<br />\n視野廣闊d"}]}